name: Dark Grey Little Logo Zip Up Hoody
description:
New for Autumn Winter 2013. 

Overview – A men's regular fit dark grey crew neck organic cotton zip-up hoody with the Subtle logo printed in burgundy on the chest.

Details - The zip-up hoody has been certified 100% organic cotton by the Soil Association, and constructed in a factory, which uses renewable energy and does not use child labour or forced labour. The logo has been screen printed by hand onto the zip-up hoody with plastisol ink on Tyneside. 

Fit - Our regular fit is a straight up and down cut with a zip in the centre of the garment. The hoody fits loosely round the torso.

Sizes - Small - 36 to 38 inch chest. We currently have none in stock. 
Medium - 38 to 40 inch chest. We currently have none in stock. 
Large - 40 to 42 inch chest. We currently have none in stock. 
Extra Large - 42 to 44 inch chest x 1.

Photo – The model wears a large. 

Care - The garment should be washed on a 30 degree wash, and washed with dark colours only. It should be reshaped whilst damp, ironed on one spot, and the print should not be ironed over.

Looks good with - A pair of jeans or chinos with a pair of trainers or shoes. How you show your plumage is optional.
